- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is relevant as the paper proposes the use of neural object detection architectures for trajectory following. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper proposes a novel framework for autonomous navigation. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with control of mobile robots.
